org.jetel.util.file

Class TrueZipVFSEntries

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.util.file.TrueZipVFSEntries

  • public class TrueZipVFSEntries
extends java.lang.Object
    This class registers all archives managed by TrueZip library for a single graph instance. It is used to explicitly flush all the archives to disk after graph execution is done, so that the archives can be accessed in the same JVM by other code than TrueZip.
